# Astro env-var contract for Phase 3 analytics.
# PUBLIC_ prefix is REQUIRED — without it, import.meta.env.PUBLIC_POSTHOG_KEY
# resolves to undefined in client-side code (Pitfall 2 in 03-RESEARCH.md).
#
# Local dev: copy this file to .env.local and paste the project API key.
# Vercel: set PUBLIC_POSTHOG_KEY across Production / Preview / Development scopes.
# See User-Action Item 2 in .planning/phases/03-analytics-forms-notifications/03-RESEARCH.md.
PUBLIC_POSTHOG_KEY=
